# emprac

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of emprac is to practice building a package in R.

## Installation

You can install the development version of emprac from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

```{r results='hide'}
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("phille10/emprac")
```
